GROUP BY	Groups rows with the same values for aggregate calculations.
HAVING	Filters grouped records based on aggregate conditions.
WHERE vs HAVING	WHERE filters rows before grouping; HAVING filters groups after grouping.
Aggregate vs Scalar Functions	Aggregate functions work on multiple rows; scalar functions work on individual values.
ROLLUP / CUBE	ROLLUP generates hierarchical subtotals; CUBE generates all possible subtotal combinations.


